Interface CPCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface CPCommand
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'CP Command'. Comando asosciato al Content Panel che viene eseguito a seconda di quanto specificato in execute.

    The following features are supported:

    • Execute
    • Command
